          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马谡，你方才言道：家有八旬老母，无人侍奉。你死之后，将你钱粮拔与你老"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母名下，为养老之费。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马谡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢丞相，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马谡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马谡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参谋！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马谡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武侯！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马谡 （对哭） 哎哎……"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，斩！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（手下允，押马谡下，开刀。龙套上，献首级。）"
