          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我哭一声马参谋，叫一声马幼常，吓吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "丞相为何泪如麻？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相，今日斩了马谡，为何流泪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，老将军，我想先帝白帝城托孤之时，言道：马谡言过其实，总无大用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山人一时大意，错用了马谡，失守街亭。我哭得先主，何曾哭得马谡？待山人"
        },
        {
